{{! This virtual outlet is designed to detect when the sump water level has been too low for an extended }}
{{! period of time. This is to help prevent turning things on and off with small fluctuations }}
{{! in the sensor when at the threshold limits of the sensor. }}
Fallback OFF
Set OFF
{{! If the sump water low sensor triggers, turn this virtual outlet on. }}
If {{apexModules.sump_water_low_optical_sensor.moduleName}} OPEN Then ON
{{! Wait for the outlet to be ON for 1 minute before actually triggering it on. }}
Defer {{apexVariables.ONE_MINUTE}} Then ON